    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-Shell" data-lang="Shell"><span class="line"><span class="cl">apt-get update
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">apt-get install docker-ce docker-ce-cli containerd.io docker-compose-plugin</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h2 id="启动-docker">启动 docker</h2>
