    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-Shell" data-lang="Shell"><span class="line"><span class="cl">service <span class="nb">enable</span> docker
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">service start docker
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># wsl2 ubuntu 22.04 启动报错，执行以下命令修复</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># update-alternatives --set iptables /usr/sbin/iptables-legacy</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="c1"># update-alternatives --set ip6tables /usr/sbin/ip6tables-legacy</span></span></span></code></pre></div></div>
